---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Manon Bart">
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>about_me</h2>

        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="/icons/manon-photo.png" alt="Portrait of Manon Bart">
                <p class="photo-caption"></p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-text">
                <p>Hello everyone, this is Manon. Encapsulated here is a little bit of my favorite things: my research, my fun code projects, and my personal hobbies in travelling, math, science and the arts.</p>

                <p>I grew up in the beautiful state of Louisiana, where I studied chemical engineering and physics at Louisiana State University and then completed my doctorate in theoretical physics at Tulane University in 2025. My PhD involved studying classical and quantum optical communications and computing. During my studies, I used AI to deploy, refine and improve these optical technologies. I also worked at NASA Goddard in D.C. during this time.</p>

                <p>Since graduating, I have been based in Namur, Belgium for my Postdoc. I am currently working at the University of Namur studying AI for optical archaeometric techniques as part of the PHOENIX project. I am lucky enough to use these techniques to study parchments, 5th century BC coins from the city of Argos in Greece, and 16th century book bindings from the Plantin printing press. </p>

                <p>I hope you stay for a little while! And feel free to connect with me on LinkedIn, Github or through my email!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .about-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
        gap: 2.5rem;
        align-items: start;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .about-image img {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 28px -18px color-mix(in srgb, var(--moss) 50%, transparent);
    }

    .photo-caption {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        color: var(--ink-soft);
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
    }

    .about-text p { margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
    .about-text p:first-child::first-letter {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--moss);
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
        .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .about-image { max-width: 300px; margin: 0 auto; }
    }
</style>
